lead_paragraph: Veteran Rod Pampling almost shot golf’s magic number before settling for an 11-under-par 60 in the opening round at the Shriners Hospitals for Children Open in Las Vegas on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Aussie Pampling Cards 60 for Two-Shot Lead in Las Vegas
